isk\n|Diss Track on Emiway Bantai\n|-\n|2018\n|Ready For My Vyah<ref>{{Citation|last=Raftaar|title=Ready For My Vyah (Shaadi Anthem) {{!}} Raftaar {{!}} Deep Kalsi {{!}} Akriti Kakar {{!}} Ft. Sonia Mann|date=1 December 2018|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-D2lQRND9zQ|access-date=1 December 2018}}</ref>\n|Deep Kalsi, Akriti Kakar and Raftaar\n|Deep Kalsi\n|Shaadi Anthem\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2019\n|[[Naachne Ka Shaunq|Nachne Ka Shaunq]]\n|Raftaar and [[Brodha V]]\n|Raftaar and [[Brodha V]]\n|\n|-\n|[[Main Wahi Hoon]]\n|Raftaar and KARMA\n|Raftaar\n|\n|-\n|2019\n|Dilli Waali Baatcheet\n|Raftaar\n|Raftaar\n|\n|-\n|2020\n|Aage Chal\n|Raftaar\n|Saurabh Lokhande\n|Journey on Raftaar Life\n|-\n|2020\n|Me and My Pen\n|Raftaar Ft. Shah Rule\n|Raftaar and Shah Rule\n|Intro of Mr. Nair\n|}\n\n===Films===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#cfc; text-align:center;\"\n| '''Year''' || '''Film(s)''' || '''Song(s)''' || '''Composer(s)'''||'''Lyrics(s)'''|| '''Co-singer(s)'''||'''Notes'''\n|- \n|2013\n|''[[Bullet Raja]]''\n|\"Tamanchey Pe Disco\"\n|[[RDB (band)|RDB]], [[Manj Musik]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Raftaar\n|Nindy Kaur, Manj Musik, RDB\n|rowspan=\"13\"|Hindi film \n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|2014\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Heropanti]]''\n|\"Whistle Baja\"\n|Manj Musik, [[Laxmikant Pyarelal]]\n|Manj Musik, Nindy Kaur\n|-\n|\"The Puppy Song\"\n|Manj Musik \n|Manj Musik\n|-\n|''[[Fugly (film)|Fugly]]''\n|\"Dhup Chik\"\n|Raftaar \n|[[Badshah (rapper)|Badshah]], [[Aastha Gill]]\n|-\n|''[[Dr. Cabbie]]''\n|\"Dal Makhni\"\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Manj Musik\n|Manj Musik, Raftaar\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Manj Musik\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2015\n|''[[Gabbar is Back]]''\n|\"Warna Gabbar Aa Jayega\"\n|Manj Musik, Raftaar, Big Dhillon\n|-\n|''[[Singh Is Bliing]]''\n|\"Singh and Kaur\"\n|Manj Musik, Nindy Kaur, Raftaar, Big Dhillon\n|Manj Musik, Nindy Kaur\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|2016\n|''[[Baaghi (2016 film)|Baaghi]]''\n|\"Let's Talk About Love\"\n|Raftaar, [[Shabbir Khan]]\n|[[Neha Kakkar]]\n|-\n|''[[A Flying Jatt]]''